HEADWORD: Forwards
<hw>For"wards</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>
}</mhw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>forweard</ets>,
<ets>foreweard</ets>; <ets>for</ets>, <ets>fore</ets> +
<ets>-weardes</ets>; akin to G. <ets>vorw⟦aum⟧rts</ets>. The <it>s</it>
is properly a genitive ending. See <er>For</er>, <er>Fore</er>, and
<er>-ward</er>, <er>-wards</er>.]</ety> <def>Toward a part or place
